    Note over Dev,Registry: Flow 1: Bundle Build and Release

    Dev->>GH: Push / PR<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: GitHub Token
    GH->>Konflux: Webhook trigger (PaC)<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Webhook Secret
    Konflux->>Sources: Fetch provenance (bundle_build_args.map)<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: GitHub Token
    Konflux->>Quay: Push odh-operator-bundle image<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Push Credentials
    EC->>Konflux: Verify SLSA provenance<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Service Account

    Note over Dev,Registry: Flow 2: Catalog (FBC) Build

    Konflux->>GH: Build nudge updates catalog-patch.yaml<br/>Git, Auth: GitHub Token
    Konflux->>Quay: Push rhoai-fbc-fragment image<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Push Credentials

    Note over Dev,Registry: Flow 3: Operator Installation (Runtime)

    OLM->>Quay: Pull FBC catalog fragment<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Pull Secret
    OLM->>Quay: Pull operator bundle image<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Pull Secret
    OLM->>Cluster: Install CSV + CRDs + RBAC<br/>Kubernetes API, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
    Cluster->>Cluster: rhods-operator starts<br/>Auth: SA token<br/>(redhat-ods-operator-controller-manager)
    Cluster->>Registry: Pull component images<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Pull Secret

    Note over Cluster: Disconnected: Uses ImageDigestMirrorSet<br/>registry.redhat.io/rhoai -> quay.io/rhoai
